metadata.title: ADAM elements 5-in-1 USB C Hub - 4K USB C to HDMI - SD Card Reader - 2 USB 3.1 Ports - Portable, Durable Aluminum Case
features: FULL FUNCTION HUB includes 3 USB 3.1 ports, 4K HDMI and 1080p VGA outputs (simultaneous output), USB-C port with power delivery up to 100W (requires compatible USB-C port), and slots for SD and microSD cards.
SUPERIOR DURABILITY thanks to rugged, milled aluminum housing, heavy duty braided cable, extra long strain reliefs — this hub is built to last.

DESIGNED AND TESTED for seamless connection to Macbooks and other USB-C equipped devices (NOTE requires full-function USB-C port — check your port for support of USB PD, HDMI output, etc. before purchase).

SHIELDED CONNECTOR and cable blocks interference between USB and WIFI - Using your A08 USB hub won’t kill your WIFI connection thanks to its seamless USB-C connector with tough, lightweight tinned steel casing.

WORKS WITH Macbook Pro & other Apple laptops, iPad Pro, PC laptops (requires full function USB-C port — check your model), Microsoft Surface series, HP Folio and other Windows tablets, some Android devices (check your model).
